{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "rentread-api-collection-001",
    "name": "RentRead API Collection",
    "description": "Complete Postman collection for testing the RentRead Online Book Rental REST API.\n\nBase URL: http://localhost:8081\nAuth: HTTP Basic Authentication\n\n## Testing Order:\n1. Register Admin & User accounts (Public)\n2. Login to verify credentials (Public)\n3. Create books as Admin (Admin Only)\n4. Browse books as User (Authenticated)\n5. Rent books as User (Authenticated)\n6. Get active rentals (Authenticated)\n7. Return books (Authenticated)\n8. Test rental limit enforcement\n9. Test authorization (User tries Admin actions)\n10. Update & Delete books as Admin",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
